{"id":310448,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/蘋果日報-庭外熱議-徐明送賽格威-薄瓜瓜用來把妹/","date":"2013-08-24T21:47:22Z","modified":"2013-08-24T21:47:22Z","title":"蘋果日報 | 庭外熱議 徐明送賽格威 薄瓜瓜用來把妹","content":"<p><div><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2F%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20130825%2FLA24%2FLA24_007.jpg\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20130825/35246574_87a44fc35b09a7c1049814a8bbca7f31_160x160.jpg\" /></a><span></p>\n<p>薄案開庭意外揭露八卦。檢方前天透露的證人證詞指出，大連實德集團董事長徐明送了一輛約40萬元台幣的賽格威電動車（圖2）給薄瓜瓜，薄把車改送給中國國家話劇院演員周某。</p>\n<hr class=\"clearman vanisher\"/>\n<hr class=\"clearman\"/><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2F%2Fimages%2Ftwapple%2F640pix%2F20130825%2FLA24%2FLA24_006.jpg\"><img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/thumbnail/20130825/35246574_6f555b29fd9cb51c2467a6b237433c68_160x160.jpg\" /></a><span></p>\n<p>有網友說，「周某」就是周麗，但據資料，國家話劇院只有「周莉」（圖1），沒有「周麗」，外界猜想，她可能就是薄瓜瓜想把的妹。<br />◎大陸中心</p>\n<hr class=\"clearman\"/><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://redirect.viglink.com?key=11fe087258b6fc0532a5ccfc924805c0&#038;u=mailto%3Aonlineopinions%40appledaily.com.tw%3Fsubject%3D%25A6%25B3%25B8%25DC%25ADn%25BB%25A1%25A7%25EB%25BDZ%25A1u%25A7Y%25AE%25C9%25BD%25D7%25BE%25C2%25A1v\">有話要說 投稿「即時論壇」</p>\n<p>onlineopinions@appledaily.com.tw</p>\n<p></a></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dFc0V1d0REQ4RkJ5d25uWFowVTNhWUE6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"328\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form me